<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Our Community</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4f46e5;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .credentials {
            background-color: #f0f4ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4f46e5;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Our Community, <%= userName %>!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>We're thrilled to have you join our MERN Stack Chat Community. Your account has been successfully created!</p>
        
        <div class="credentials">
            <h3>Your Account Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Username:</strong> <%= userName %></p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
            <p><strong>Password:</strong> (the one you set during registration)</p>
            <p><strong>Gender:</strong> <%= gender %></p>
            <% if (profileImage) { %>
                <p><strong>Profile Image:</strong> <a href="<%= profileImage %>">View Image</a></p>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        
        <p>To get started, you can login to your account using the credentials above.</p>
        
        <a href="<%= FRONTEND_URL %>/login" class="button">Login to Your Account</a>
        
        <p>For security reasons, we recommend changing your password after your first login.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you didn't create this account, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
        <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> MERN Stack Chat Community. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>